<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>At Dental C, we respect and protect your privacy. We collect personal details such as your name,
    contact information, medical and dental history, treatment records, and payment details to provide safe dental care, 
    process billing and insurance, and communicate with you about appointments or treatments. 
    Your information is kept secure and is only shared when necessary, such as with healthcare providers, 
    insurance companies, or as required by law. We do not sell your data, 
    and only authorized staff or trusted service providers may access it under strict confidentiality.
    You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your information, subject to legal requirements.</p>
